data.description: This is a beautifully updated 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom townhouse located in Phoenix just minutes from Desert Ridge, the Biltmore and Downtown Phoenix.  Outside the front door is a courtyard perfect for playing, having a picnic or to walk your pet.  This home features granite countertops, white cabinets, and grey wood porcelain tile.  You will love the vaulted ceilings and modern charm.  Enjoy sitting out on your private back patio that has synthetic grass.  Such a great use of space.
